      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional character and proven reliability. This model has been curated to maintain its mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal, offering a sophisticated driving experience. Rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our standards for performance and safety, it stands as a premier choice for those seeking quality and value in a pre-owned executive transport.",
      "price": 34500.0,
